            <thetext>Some SVN clients do not create a directory if the directory is empty. Although we can create a README file or something in the directory stating that there are no translation files necessary, it would be nice if the generator made existence of the translation folder non-mandatory so that if it were missing, the project would build anyway.</thetext>
